narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: All resources were available and functional - but the course budget needs to be greater (even more so than for other fabrication electives).

The shop was of course a fabulous resource. I did have to buy my own sewing machine for the upholstery but otherwise the lab downstairs more than met my needs. The $200 budget is entirely too low for the type of pieces that are expected in the class.
all of the resources were provided.
